n></p> <p> <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Hotline:&nbsp;0971 02 66 78</span></strong></span></span></p> <p> <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: black;\">Điện thoại</span></strong><span style=\"color: black;\">&nbsp;: 04 62 60 44 63</span></span></span></p> <p> <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: black;\">Email</span></strong><span style=\"color: black;\">: info@vnglaw.vn</span></span></span></p> <p> <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: black;\">Website</span></strong><span style=\"color: black;\">:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://vnglaw.com/vi-VN/t100c341/Trang-chu.htm\">www.vnglaw.com</a></span></span></p> <p align=\"left\"> <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\"><strong>Facebook:&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/V%C4%83n-ph%C3%B2ng-Lu%E1%BA%ADt-s%C6%B0-VNG-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam-555960664569674/\">https://www.facebook.com/Văn-ph&ograve;ng-luật-sư-VNG-Việt-Nam-555960664569674/</a></span></span></p>', 'thanh-lap-doanh-nghiep-tai-ha-nam', '/User_folder_upload/userfiles/images/ha nam.jpg', 'VNG Law tư vấn miễn ph&#237; v&#224; hỗ trợ qu&#253; kh&#225;ch h&#224;ng c&#243; nhu cầu th&#224;nh lập doanh nghiệp tại H&#224; Nam với thời gian nhanh nhất v&#224; mức chi ph&#237; hợp l&#253; nhất.');
